headline: DoorDash and Coco Expand Global Partnership with U.S. Sidewalk Robot Delivery Launch
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, April 10, 2025--DoorDash and Coco Robotics announced an expansion of their partnership to offer sidewalk robot delivery for DoorDash customers in L.A. and Chicago.
